'''圣保罗堂'''（{{lang-de|Pauluskirche}}）是[[瑞士|瑞士]][[伯尔尼|伯尔尼]]的一个[[归正会|归正会]]教堂，由瑞士建筑师卡尔·莫瑟建于1902年到1905年，采用[[新艺术运动|新艺术运动]]风格<ref name='Applica'>{{Cite document | title = Applica 5 | publisher = Parish of St. Paul's, Bern | pages = 34–36 | year = 2009 | id =  | url = http://www.sax.ch/assets/files/Pauluskirche%20Bern.pdf | journal =  | access-date = 2020-08-07 | archive-date = 2021-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210118015237/https://www.sax.ch/assets/files/Pauluskirche%20Bern.pdf }}</ref>。它已被列入[[瑞士国家和区域重要文化财产名录|瑞士国家和区域重要文化财产名录]]，是该国新艺术运动风格的最佳例子之一。<ref name=godyhofmann>{{cite web |url=http://www.godyhofmann.ch/bauten_paulus.html |title=Pauluskirche Bern |publisher=Gody Hofmann |date= |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2018-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181220101208/http://godyhofmann.ch/bauten_paulus.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Teller2010">{{cite book|author=Matthew Teller|title=The Rough Guide to Switzerland|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Xhoug6rVIBkC&pg=PA208|accessdate=11 February 2012|date=4 May 2010|publisher=Rough Guides Ltd|isbn=978-1-84836-471-4|page=208}}</ref> 钟楼高36米，有5口钟。教堂[[立面|立面]]的[[浮雕|浮雕]]描绘持剑的[[使徒保罗|使徒保罗]]。花窗玻璃由来自[[勒拉赫|勒拉赫]]的艺术家马克斯·莱格完成<ref>{{cite book|title= Historisch-topographisches Lexikon der Stadt Bern|last= Weber|first= Berchtold|year= 1976|url= http://www.digibern.ch/weber/weber_pq.html|accessdate= 2011-03-27|archive-date= 2002-06-24|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20020624204855/http://www.digibern.ch/weber/weber_pq.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。内部采用蓝色和绿色色调，和丰富的金色装饰画。<ref name='Applica' />

